Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(602,542)}It's the World Duel Carnival Tournament Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(646,544)}The time has finally come to decide the best in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(616,557)}Out of the 23 best Duelists who survived the preliminaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(613,549)}Here goes! I'm aiming for Duel Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, the fireworks are starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the Duel Carnival Tournament Finals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, get up alr-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, in order to make sure he definitely isn't late,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he slept outside the entrance to Heartland all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was so pumped up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma is experiencing the importance of this tournament in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cleaning. Idiot's room. Cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(630,66)}The fireworks have announced the start of the World Duel Carnival-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that Kaito fellow's pretty hot too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only 23 remaining among more than 10,000 participants.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be an awesome tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They're all incredible Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who will win the championship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IV for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you sleeping out {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still half-alseep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, he thinks this is his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a wild kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up and open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Heartland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the starting day of the World Duel Carnival Tournament Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Carnival...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup, yup, yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it would've been bad if I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there was no point in sleeping in front of the entrance, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the opening ceremony is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh crap, crap, crap!\N - Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna Duel here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean some kind of Field Magic has been casted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, this is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart Burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now declare the start of the World Duel Carnival Tournament Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first stage will be the Park Section!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we will Duel using this entire Heartland as the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going by the name Duel Coasters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Coasters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, they Duel using those roller coasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't it sound interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, bring on whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a shame if I can't enjoy this, seeing as how I made it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuma, aren't you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too late for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then, the 23 Duelists who won in the preliminaries to get here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Muster up every bit of your intellect and your strength to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,482)}Number 51: "Here we come, Tournament Finals! \NDuel Coasters, Go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And set that prestigious title of first ever World Duel Champion as your goal!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,522)}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are the Duel Coasters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get hurt badly if you get too worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Coasters are no game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, what Droite said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a true showdown that puts our lives on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But be sure to enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's IV! IV!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}, please, you must take good care of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital, stop time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to search for those holding Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But if you do that, you'll end up revealing yourself to Number Holders instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0.1 seconds is good enough! Hurry and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He noticed after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did your job, so get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, some awesome members are gathered here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among them are Kaito and Shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And excluding Tron and his group,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is bound to be a number of powerful opponents here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so freaking cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting pumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's our prey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then we'll start with a small deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rest comes when you complete your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the target is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy named Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you must retrieve those Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now! Soon enough, we will fire the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fellow warriors, prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These Duel Coasters will link to your D-Pads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision - Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the time has come to bet your lives in these Coasters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Heart Pieces you all gathered during the preliminaries
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will act as the starting key for the Duel Coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set your Heart Pieces in the designated location in the cockpit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's a map, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the? There's M and T marks all over the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Magic" and "Traps"... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is well thought out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone! Gone, gone! My Heart Pieces're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd I leave them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma keeps looking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the mental pressure made him snap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he fooling around at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... He doesn't seem to be fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cleaning done. Cleaning done. Found heart in idiot's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This. This.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart Pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart Pieces're gone! What'll I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma! Akari-{\i0}san{\i1} just contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They found your Heart Pieces in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're on there way to Heartland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sis did?! I owe her one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay there, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah!\N - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has now come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall now drop the curtain on this stage of battle that will determine the best in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?! They didn't make it in time at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We start in ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Heart Pieces!\N - Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Only one, Contestant Yuma Tsukumo's Coaster, didn't start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he encounter some trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They left! Hurry and get here, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, she won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your Heart Pieces! Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's moving! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why are you in here too, Kotori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was running and I ended up in here before I realized it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't get off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, the two of us will have to fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an unexpected development!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contestant Yuma, who had a delayed start, has ridden into view with a girl in tow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Coasters were originally made for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as the founder of this tournament,\N I shall personally permit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is feels amazing! Coasters are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that! I've already fallen far behind the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we Duel in these things when you can't even find your opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm riding on one lane all by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's two Coasters riding one land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, move, move! I'll send anyone in my way flying like a bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Heroic Challenger - Spartas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My opponent's got Blood Storm. Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just activate the Magic Card Force from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card's effect halves Blood Storm's Attack Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and increases Spartas' Attack Points by the same amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Attack him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight Javelin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take even one wrong step here, we'll suffer heavy injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ten years too early to be riding in front of my lane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:15:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're on the same lane as someone else, you have to Duel them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you can switch lanes freely if you wish to fight the person you encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Jaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Scream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... That's Shark for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness... Where's Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting on quite the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away, IV!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to utterly crush you in this tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big mouth for such a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Gimmick Puppet - Bomb Egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone, trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, he's always lusting for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite having no idea what kind of prolonged battle awaits us in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, rather than battling, I should invest all my attention toward protecting and increasing my Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are in my way! Move at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send him flying, Vylon Disigma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attac-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who dare to come close to me shall be consumed by Hell's Inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Trap Card, Sun of the Abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster holding 2000 or more Attack Points attacks me directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this card deals the opposing player 800 points of damage for each card he holds in his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, this is a 'Magic Point'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, the set card was the God of Healing, Dian Keto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effect of this card increases my Life Points by 1000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, V.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IV and Shark are both fighting relentlessly with all of their might.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Yuma Tsukumo faring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so strong! Man, I so wanna start Dueling already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish may soon me granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I just passed them by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this guy's late start,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don’t need to lure him out from the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we gotta do is crush him like we promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be rolling in dough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I will pay you as much money as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only {\i1}after{\i0} you show me just how strong Yuma Tsukumo really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! As we planned before, we'll use Formation One!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're catching up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly they've been waiting to ambush you, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're attacking from both sides to prevent you from escaping to the side lanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! I'm gonna get away from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a 'T' mark up ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trap Card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Underground Machine Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It deals 200 points of damage for every card you have in your hand and on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that so calmly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they set Magic and Trap Cards throughout the course?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he didn't notice such an obvious trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Dueling skills must not be anything to brag about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let’s finish him off as soon as possible so we can go home and count our cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, kid. Duel against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Formation Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They caught up so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Magnet Eagle Delta from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Magnet Saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Magnet Saucer as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They already Summoned Monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's three-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has become a three-on-one battle from the get-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:22:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Duel Coaster's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a testament of the World Duel Carnival Final?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's see it, Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how strong are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:23:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge battle is underway between the Finalists who made it to the Coasters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Duel Coasters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:24:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the beginning, a trio named Fallguys have ambushed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I was in a desperate situation, she...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, they're aiming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lane's been blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's their team play!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Coasters Vs the Rampaging Train!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why the heck are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur is a sword wielded by a king long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.90,0:24:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's got nothing to do with the Great Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.48,0:24:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say Great Me, I said King.\N (Note: {\i1}oresama{\i0}, {\i1}ousama{\i0})
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.48,0:24:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tryin' ta' praise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.44,0:24:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}Osaka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.90,0:24:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You best be cuttin' it out!
